<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" itunes:timing="Word"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><ttm:agent type="other" xml:id="v2"/><iTunesMetadata xmlns="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal"><songwriters><songwriter>Anders Wikström</songwriter><songwriter>Fredrik Thomander</songwriter></songwriters></iTunesMetadata><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Firefly"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="A*Teens"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Teen Spirit (Bonus Version)"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="2605141971"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="42886855"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="ArSrNa"/></metadata></head><body dur="3:04.908"><div begin="17.883" end="3:04.908"><p begin="17.883" end="19.787" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="17.883" end="18.230">When</span> <span begin="18.230" end="18.579">I</span> <span begin="18.579" end="18.891">said</span> <span begin="18.891" end="19.787">go</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我说要走</span></p><p begin="20.139" end="22.511" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="20.139" end="20.431">I</span> <span begin="20.431" end="20.759">ne</span><span begin="20.759" end="21.132">ver</span> <span begin="21.132" end="21.544">meant</span> <span begin="21.544" end="22.511">away</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不等于我要离开</span></p><p begin="23.787" end="25.443" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="23.787" end="24.119">You</span> <span begin="24.119" end="24.473">ought</span> <span begin="24.473" end="24.832">to</span> <span begin="24.832" end="25.443">know</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你该懂</span></p><p begin="25.930" end="29.290" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="25.930" end="26.266">The</span> <span begin="26.266" end="27.043">freaky</span> <span begin="27.043" end="27.382">games</span> <span begin="27.382" end="27.693">we</span> <span begin="27.693" end="29.290">play</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这只是我们之间的任性游戏</span></p><p begin="29.624" end="31.733" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="29.624" end="29.916">Could</span> <span begin="29.916" end="30.271">you</span> <span begin="30.271" end="31.733">forgive</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">原谅我吧</span></p><p begin="31.733" end="34.503" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="31.733" end="32.095">And</span> <span begin="32.095" end="32.454">learn</span> <span begin="32.454" end="32.833">how</span> <span begin="32.833" end="33.175">to</span> <span begin="33.175" end="34.503">forget</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">忘掉这些</span></p><p begin="35.142" end="39.459" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="35.142" end="35.409">Hear</span> <span begin="35.409" end="35.781">me</span> <span begin="35.781" end="36.129">as</span> <span begin="36.129" end="36.499">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="36.499" end="37.260">calling</span> <span begin="37.260" end="37.586">out</span> <span begin="37.586" end="37.944">your</span> <span begin="37.944" end="39.459">name</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">听我呼唤，你的名字</span></p><p begin="40.932" end="43.786" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="40.932" end="41.675">Fire</span><span begin="41.675" end="41.983">fly</span> <span begin="41.983" end="42.359">come</span> <span begin="42.359" end="42.718">back</span> <span begin="42.718" end="43.051">to</span> <span begin="43.051" end="43.786">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">萤火虫啊，快回来</span></p><p begin="43.786" end="46.758" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="43.786" end="44.140">Make</span> <span begin="44.140" end="44.525">the</span> <span begin="44.525" end="44.884">night</span> <span begin="44.884" end="45.279">as</span> <span begin="45.279" end="45.661">bright</span> <span begin="45.661" end="46.023">as</span> <span begin="46.023" end="46.758">day</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">让我的夜晚(重新)亮如白昼</span></p><p begin="46.758" end="49.699" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="46.758" end="47.120">I&apos;ll</span> <span begin="47.120" end="47.487">be</span> <span begin="47.487" end="48.237">looking</span> <span begin="48.237" end="48.589">out</span> <span begin="48.589" end="48.925">for</span> <span begin="48.925" end="49.699">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我要眺望你的身影</span></p><p begin="49.699" end="52.629" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="49.699" end="50.036">Tell</span> <span begin="50.036" end="50.396">me</span> <span begin="50.396" end="50.756">that</span> <span begin="50.756" end="51.127">you&apos;re</span> <span begin="51.127" end="51.823">lonely</span> <span begin="51.823" end="52.629">too</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你要告诉我你也孤独</span></p><p begin="52.629" end="55.555" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="52.629" end="53.376">Fire</span><span begin="53.376" end="53.685">fly</span> <span begin="53.685" end="54.069">come</span> <span begin="54.069" end="54.423">lead</span> <span begin="54.423" end="54.770">me</span> <span begin="54.770" end="55.555">on</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">萤火虫啊，引领我</span></p><p begin="55.555" end="58.463" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="55.555" end="56.314">Follow</span> <span begin="56.314" end="56.658">you</span> <span begin="56.658" end="57.033">in</span><span begin="57.033" end="57.360">to</span> <span begin="57.360" end="57.732">the</span> <span begin="57.732" end="58.463">sun</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">跟着你，入太阳</span></p><p begin="58.463" end="1:01.408" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="58.463" end="58.827">That&apos;s</span> <span begin="58.827" end="59.175">the</span> <span begin="59.175" end="59.561">way</span> <span begin="59.561" end="59.941">it</span> <span begin="59.941" end="1:00.275">ought</span> <span begin="1:00.275" end="1:00.632">to</span> <span begin="1:00.632" end="1:01.408">be</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这才是，它该走的路径</span></p><p begin="1:01.408" end="1:06.771" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:01.408" end="1:02.118">Fire</span><span begin="1:02.118" end="1:02.454">fly</span> <span begin="1:02.454" end="1:02.844">come</span> <span begin="1:02.844" end="1:03.610">back</span> <span begin="1:03.610" end="1:03.935">to</span> <span begin="1:03.935" end="1:04.498">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">萤火虫啊，快回来</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="1:04.215" end="1:06.771"><span begin="1:04.215" end="1:05.169">(Fly</span> <span begin="1:05.441" end="1:05.739">fire</span><span begin="1:05.739" end="1:06.771">fly)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">萤火虫</span></span></p><p begin="1:08.058" end="1:09.874" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:08.058" end="1:08.325">You</span> <span begin="1:08.325" end="1:08.732">and</span> <span begin="1:08.732" end="1:09.486">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你和我</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="1:08.868" end="1:09.874"><span begin="1:08.868" end="1:09.235">(You</span> <span begin="1:09.235" end="1:09.500">and</span> <span begin="1:09.500" end="1:09.874">me)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你和我</span></span></p><p begin="1:09.874" end="1:12.299" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:09.874" end="1:10.187">We</span> <span begin="1:10.187" end="1:10.534">shared</span> <span begin="1:10.534" end="1:10.907">a</span> <span begin="1:10.907" end="1:12.299">mystery</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">共享神秘</span></p><p begin="1:13.481" end="1:15.604" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:13.481" end="1:13.902">We</span> <span begin="1:13.902" end="1:14.232">were</span> <span begin="1:14.232" end="1:14.552">so</span> <span begin="1:14.552" end="1:15.604">close</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们那么紧密</span></p><p begin="1:15.849" end="1:18.537" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:15.849" end="1:16.126">Like</span> <span begin="1:16.126" end="1:16.771">honey</span> <span begin="1:16.771" end="1:17.119">to</span> <span begin="1:17.119" end="1:17.416">the</span> <span begin="1:17.416" end="1:18.537">bee</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如同蜜与蜂</span></p><p begin="1:19.285" end="1:21.125" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:19.285" end="1:19.685">And</span> <span begin="1:19.685" end="1:20.055">if</span> <span begin="1:20.055" end="1:20.417">you</span> <span begin="1:20.417" end="1:20.788">tell</span> <span begin="1:20.788" end="1:21.125">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果你告诉我</span></p><p begin="1:21.125" end="1:24.475" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:21.125" end="1:21.483">How</span> <span begin="1:21.483" end="1:21.857">to</span> <span begin="1:21.857" end="1:22.205">make</span> <span begin="1:22.205" end="1:22.582">you</span> <span begin="1:22.582" end="1:23.325">under</span><span begin="1:23.325" end="1:24.475">stand</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">怎样才能让你明白我意</span></p><p begin="1:24.475" end="1:29.090" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:24.475" end="1:24.817">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="1:24.817" end="1:25.549">minor</span> <span begin="1:25.549" end="1:25.891">in</span> <span begin="1:25.891" end="1:26.222">a</span> <span begin="1:26.222" end="1:26.988">major</span> <span begin="1:26.988" end="1:27.348">kind</span> <span begin="1:27.348" end="1:27.668">of</span> <span begin="1:27.668" end="1:29.090">way</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我这小调般的性格也能奏出明亮的声音</span></p><p begin="1:30.703" end="1:33.554" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:30.703" end="1:31.418">Fire</span><span begin="1:31.418" end="1:31.731">fly</span> <span begin="1:31.731" end="1:32.103">come</span> <span begin="1:32.103" end="1:32.448">back</span> <span begin="1:32.448" end="1:32.805">to</span> <span begin="1:32.805" end="1:33.554">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">萤火虫啊，快回来</span></p><p begin="1:33.554" end="1:36.503" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:33.554" end="1:33.912">Make</span> <span begin="1:33.912" end="1:34.279">the</span> <span begin="1:34.279" end="1:34.639">night</span> <span begin="1:34.639" end="1:35.023">as</span> <span begin="1:35.023" end="1:35.365">bright</span> <span begin="1:35.365" end="1:35.752">as</span> <span begin="1:35.752" end="1:36.503">day</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">让这黑夜亮如白昼</span></p><p begin="1:36.503" end="1:39.443" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:36.503" end="1:36.885">I&apos;ll</span> <span begin="1:36.885" end="1:37.269">be</span> <span begin="1:37.269" end="1:38.041">looking</span> <span begin="1:38.041" end="1:38.343">out</span> <span begin="1:38.343" end="1:38.709">for</span> <span begin="1:38.709" end="1:39.443">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我会在门前眺望你的身影</span></p><p begin="1:39.443" end="1:42.360" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:39.443" end="1:39.810">Tell</span> <span begin="1:39.810" end="1:40.181">me</span> <span begin="1:40.181" end="1:40.548">that</span> <span begin="1:40.548" end="1:40.890">you&apos;re</span> <span begin="1:40.890" end="1:41.593">lonely</span> <span begin="1:41.593" end="1:42.360">too</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">告诉我，你也孤独</span></p><p begin="1:42.360" end="1:45.326" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:42.360" end="1:43.126">Fire</span><span begin="1:43.126" end="1:43.478">fly</span> <span begin="1:43.478" end="1:43.835">come</span> <span begin="1:43.835" end="1:44.169">lead</span> <span begin="1:44.169" end="1:44.528">me</span> <span begin="1:44.528" end="1:45.326">on</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">萤火虫啊，带我走</span></p><p begin="1:45.326" end="1:48.210" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:45.326" end="1:46.046">Follow</span> <span begin="1:46.046" end="1:46.399">you</span> <span begin="1:46.399" end="1:46.752">in</span><span begin="1:46.752" end="1:47.089">to</span> <span begin="1:47.089" end="1:47.420">the</span> <span begin="1:47.420" end="1:48.210">sun</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我要跟着你，入太阳</span></p><p begin="1:48.210" end="1:51.166" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:48.210" end="1:48.534">That&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:48.534" end="1:48.923">the</span> <span begin="1:48.923" end="1:49.303">way</span> <span begin="1:49.303" end="1:49.674">it</span> <span begin="1:49.674" end="1:50.037">ought</span> <span begin="1:50.037" end="1:50.415">to</span> <span begin="1:50.415" end="1:51.166">be</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这才是它该有的路径</span></p><p begin="1:51.166" end="1:57.716" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:51.166" end="1:51.938">Fire</span><span begin="1:51.938" end="1:52.252">fly</span> <span begin="1:52.252" end="1:52.606">come</span> <span begin="1:52.606" end="1:53.326">back</span> <span begin="1:53.326" end="1:53.674">to</span> <span begin="1:53.674" end="1:54.667">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">萤火虫啊，快回来</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="1:54.110" end="1:57.716"><span begin="1:54.110" end="1:54.791">(Fly</span> <span begin="1:54.791" end="1:55.487">fire</span><span begin="1:55.487" end="1:56.272">fly</span> <span begin="1:56.272" end="1:56.647">through</span> <span begin="1:56.647" end="1:56.980">the</span> <span begin="1:56.980" end="1:57.716">sky)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">飞吧，萤火虫，穿过天空</span></span></p><p begin="1:57.716" end="2:03.549" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:57.716" end="1:58.209">Come</span> <span begin="1:58.209" end="1:58.522">and</span> <span begin="1:58.522" end="1:58.850">play</span> <span begin="1:58.850" end="1:59.180">with</span> <span begin="1:59.180" end="1:59.523">my</span> <span begin="1:59.523" end="2:01.874">desire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">来和我的思念共舞</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="2:00.566" end="2:03.549"><span begin="2:00.566" end="2:00.936">(Don&apos;t</span> <span begin="2:00.936" end="2:01.367">be</span> <span begin="2:01.367" end="2:02.110">long</span> <span begin="2:02.110" end="2:02.458">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="2:02.458" end="2:02.818">ask</span> <span begin="2:02.818" end="2:03.549">why)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不要让我久等，也不要问为什么</span></span></p><p begin="2:03.549" end="2:09.399" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:03.549" end="2:03.876">I</span> <span begin="2:03.876" end="2:04.294">can&apos;t</span> <span begin="2:04.294" end="2:04.739">wait</span> <span begin="2:04.739" end="2:05.763">another</span> <span begin="2:05.763" end="2:08.256">night</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就算是明晚，我也不能等待</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="2:05.728" end="2:09.399"><span begin="2:05.728" end="2:06.479">(Fly</span> <span begin="2:06.479" end="2:07.181">fire</span><span begin="2:07.181" end="2:07.953">fly</span> <span begin="2:07.953" end="2:08.279">through</span> <span begin="2:08.279" end="2:08.590">the</span> <span begin="2:08.590" end="2:09.399">sky)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">飞吧，萤火虫，穿过天空</span></span></p><p begin="2:10.148" end="2:14.058" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:10.148" end="2:10.443">Wait</span> <span begin="2:10.443" end="2:11.580">another</span> <span begin="2:11.580" end="2:14.058">night</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不能等，明晚</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="2:12.361" end="2:13.772"><span begin="2:12.361" end="2:12.704">(Don&apos;t</span> <span begin="2:12.704" end="2:13.063">be</span> <span begin="2:13.063" end="2:13.772">long...)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不要想念...</span></span></p><p begin="2:14.580" end="2:17.520" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:14.580" end="2:15.982">Fire...</span><span begin="2:15.982" end="2:16.861">Fire</span><span begin="2:16.861" end="2:17.520">fly</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">萤火虫</span></p><p begin="2:17.519" end="2:20.358" itunes:key="L35" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="2:17.519" end="2:18.106">Fire</span><span begin="2:18.106" end="2:18.547">fly</span> <span begin="2:18.547" end="2:18.906">come</span> <span begin="2:18.906" end="2:19.244">back</span> <span begin="2:19.244" end="2:19.643">to</span> <span begin="2:19.643" end="2:20.358">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">萤火虫，快回来</span></p><p begin="2:20.358" end="2:23.339" itunes:key="L36" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="2:20.358" end="2:20.695">Make</span> <span begin="2:20.695" end="2:21.052">the</span> <span begin="2:21.052" end="2:21.453">night</span> <span begin="2:21.453" end="2:21.808">as</span> <span begin="2:21.808" end="2:22.152">bright</span> <span begin="2:22.152" end="2:22.486">as</span> <span begin="2:22.486" end="2:23.339">day</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">让这黑夜如白昼</span></p><p begin="2:23.339" end="2:26.268" itunes:key="L37" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:23.339" end="2:23.649">I&apos;ll</span> <span begin="2:23.649" end="2:24.038">be</span> <span begin="2:24.038" end="2:24.781">looking</span> <span begin="2:24.781" end="2:25.130">out</span> <span begin="2:25.130" end="2:25.496">for</span> <span begin="2:25.496" end="2:26.268">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我会在门口眺望你</span></p><p begin="2:26.268" end="2:29.120" itunes:key="L38" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:26.268" end="2:26.592">Tell</span> <span begin="2:26.592" end="2:26.985">me</span> <span begin="2:26.985" end="2:27.318">that</span> <span begin="2:27.318" end="2:27.684">you&apos;re</span> <span begin="2:27.684" 